{"tid":1930882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"感染武漢肺炎松鼠狗 康復岀院後兩日死亡","createTime":"2020-03-18T01:00:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T13:50:19.000Z","uid":125168,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"aac32e8ec88c921b6216ee579cce4369f5c0fd2d","tid":1930882,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T01:00:29.000Z","msg":"曾感染新型冠狀病毒的馬主周巧兒所飼養的松鼠狗死亡。漁農自然護理署表示，該松鼠狗已於周一（16日）離世，畜養人表示不願意為狗進行驗屍確定死因。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該松鼠狗曾對新冠病毒檢測呈弱陽性，自上月26日開始被送往檢疫，至3月12日及13日驗到兩次樣本結果呈陰性，其後送回予主人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200318/s00001/1584461118886/%E5%91%A8%E5%B7%A7%E5%85%92%E6%9D%BE%E9%BC%A0%E7%8B%97%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200318%2Fs00001%2F1584461118886%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25B7%25A7%25E5%2585%2592%25E6%259D%25BE%25E9%25BC%25A0%25E7%258B%2597%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25BA%25A1&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzB8ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=9cd2a885\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200318%2Fs00001%2F1584461118886%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25B7%25A7%25E5%2585%2592%25E6%259D%25BE%25E9%25BC%25A0%25E7%258B%2597%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25BA%25A1&h=35f3ccce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200318/s00001/1584461118886/%E5%91%A8%E5%B7%A7%E5%85%92%E6%9D%BE%E9%BC%A0%E7%8B%97%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%A1</a>"},{"pid":"34ee1a154da3e7c00e3561a6ad66c52201e205ec","tid":1930882,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T01:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceeda5dd04dd089ec23979769e8e47e489a40371","tid":1930882,"uid":293539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"aac32e8ec88c921b6216ee579cce4369f5c0fd2d","tid":1930882